{"type": "article", "id": 26191, "title": "自行车防盗锁", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-29T07:23:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071803183ywgJHx1UbnVSscZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">如果你打算换一个自行车锁，这款由双人设计组合 Altor 打造的 560G 是个不错的选择。它由五级钛合金制作而成，而重量（正如其名）仅为 560 克，是目前市面上最轻的高安全性自行车锁。目前它正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1282151086/560g\">Kickstarter</a> 上展开众筹，最低价为 150 美金。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180315d6t5avoq1RkOWsgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180316mEIsQoAgCLy3x7qH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180316EPZjUYxk6RravpXb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180317PopjEOkTb5KHfxC3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure></div>\n\n\n"}